          "imgtext_wordContent": "<img src=\"resource/images/5bd9deb45f925ada.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" align=\"left\" alt=\"\" />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:16px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">曲線計是用以量測地圖上曲線長度之器具。</span>\n</p>",
